    "The use of additional skip links helps in energy-efficient skip-tier communication.",
    "Moreover, the reduced number of horizontal links helps to offset the area overhead incurred in integrating additional skip links.",
    "This makes the 3D NoC in Atleus an equally practical alternative relative to the conventional and widely used 3D-mesh enabled architecture without imposing a prohibitive area overhead or excessive cost.",
